** THIS IS A WORK IN PROGRESS, NOT READY YET, but feel free to poke **

Place the WordPress folder in your CodeSniffer/Standards folder.

This requires PHP CodeSniffer:
http://pear.php.net/package/PHP_CodeSniffer/

# Check out a local copy
cd ~
git clone https://github.com/kurtpayne/wordpress-codesniffer.git

# Install to CodeSniffer
cp wordpress-codesniffer/WordPress /usr/lib/php/pear/PHP/CodeSniffer/Standards

# Run CodeSniffer
phpcs --standard=WordPress --report=full /path/to/my/files/*
